Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.74,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}こんないつもを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.91,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}吹き飛ばすきっかけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.75,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}招くばかりの指先を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:35.73,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}手のひらで重ねて
