Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:10.55,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:16.47,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:22.34,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.74,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.91,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.75,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:35.73,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:39.31,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.80,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.67,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.87,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.57,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.92,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:02:01.61,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的這一切
